  "description": "Saw-heavy suboctave bass using the bounce engine as a slap simulator — high gravity, fast rebound count, short decay. Filter cutoff low and warm. The bounce click punches like a thumb on a bass string. Phaser barely audible, just widening the low mids. Designed for the left hand.",
